    {
      "id": 691,
      "post_uuid": "0197562b-e90c-549a-1662-75842aaa1bcd",
      "title_ko": null,
      "title_zh": null,
      "content_ko": "IU-nim, my life is kind of scary right now. I have to leave my home after nine years but don’t know where to go. Money is tight. My disabled loved one depends on me. My Mom passed away recently so I’m still grieving. It’s in times like this that you are most inspiring, your music and your life. You know what it is to go through hard times and to grieve. The light that you shine gives me hope. You could have chosen different paths but instead you choose to walk in love and beauty. Thank you for your choices. Thank you for helping others to survive scary times, hard times. You are honored in my heart. I will support you and your mission as much as able for all of my years 💐💖",
      "content_zh": "IU，我现在的生活有点可怕。九年后我不得不离开家，却不知道该去哪里。经济拮据，我残疾的亲人依靠着我。妈妈最近去世了，我仍在悲伤中。正是在这样的时刻，你最能给我鼓舞，你的音乐和人生都如此。你知道经历艰难时光和悲伤是什么感觉。你散发的光芒给了我希望。你本可以选择不同的道路，却选择了爱与美好的道路。感谢你的选择。感谢你帮助他人度过可怕的、艰难的时光。你在我的心中备受敬重。我会尽我所能，在我的一生中支持你和你的使命 💐💖",
      "post_time": "2025-06-09 19:30:07",
      "image_count": 0,
      "image_urls": null,
      "local_image_paths": null,
      "likes": 0,
      "comments": 0,
      "views": 0,
      "board": "Dear. IU",
      "members_only": 0,
      "author_username": "Windbourne",
      "author_avatar": null,
      "author_local_avatar": null,
      "fan_comments": [],
      "direct_iu_replies": [
        {
          "id": 1519,
          "content_ko": "No I didn't have any other choice\nI owe it to people like you\nYou are my compass to me \nI didn't get lost because of your gaze \nI hope I am like that to you \nMay luck always await your next step. I'll keep an eye on you",
          "content_zh": "不，我别无选择\n我欠你这样的人很多\n你就是我的指南针\n因为你的目光我才没有迷失方向\n希望我也能成为你的依靠\n愿幸运永远伴随你的每一步，我会一直关注着你",
